sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant TodoConsole
participant InputValidator
participant TaskService
participant TaskRepository
participant TasksJson as tasks.json

== Delete Task ==
User->>TodoConsole: Select "Delete Task"
TodoConsole->>User: Prompt for task ID
User-->>TodoConsole: taskId
TodoConsole->>InputValidator: isValidTaskId(taskId)
alt valid input
  TodoConsole->>TaskService: deleteTask(taskId)
  TaskService->>TaskService: findTaskById(taskId)
  alt task found
    TaskService->>TaskService: remove task from vector
    TaskService->>TaskRepository: saveTasks(tasks)
    TaskRepository->>TasksJson: write updated tasks
    TasksJson-->>TaskRepository: persisted
    TaskRepository-->>TaskService: save complete
    TaskService-->>TodoConsole: true
    TodoConsole-->>User: display success
  else task not found
    TaskService-->>TodoConsole: false
    TodoConsole-->>User: display invalid ID error
  end
else invalid input
  InputValidator-->>TodoConsole: false
  TodoConsole-->>User: display validation error
end
